'''Chemex'''经典手冲咖啡壶是一个玻璃容器式的[[咖啡|咖啡]]制作器具，在1941年由移居紐約的德國[[柏林大學|柏林大學]]化學博士Peter Schlumbohm发明，多年来一直由位于[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]的Chemex公司延续制造。 

Chemex壺身的上壺與下壺合而為一，之間的壺頸用分割為兩塊的環形木頭包覆做為防燙把手，木頭以皮繩繫上。從壺頸延伸到上壺有一突起的溝槽，可做為排氣及倒出咖啡時導流之用，下壺壺身有一類似[[肚臍|肚臍]]的突起為容量標記，表示半水位的位置<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://okogreen.com.tw/blog/4216 |title=歷久不衰，誕生於二戰時期的經典濾杯—Chemex |accessdate=2018-07-23 |archive-date=2018-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723064453/https://okogreen.com.tw/blog/4216 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在1958年，[[伊利诺伊理工学院|伊利诺伊理工学院]]的设计学者认为，Chemex经典手冲咖啡壶是当今最佳设计的产品之一，并且被[[纽约|纽约]][[现代艺术博物馆|现代艺术博物馆]]收藏<ref>"Dr. Peter Schlumbohm Dead; Inventor of Coffee Maker, 66; His Chemex Called One of 100 Best Modern Devices—300 Items Patented" ''The New York Times''; November 07, 1962 [https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=F00B17FC3454157B93C5A9178AD95F468685F9]</ref><ref>"Chemex Coffee Makers" [http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/access/66382871.html?dids=66382871:66382871&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jan+08%2C+1989&author=DAVID+LASKER&pub=Los+Angeles+Times+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&desc=AROUND+HOME+Chemex+Coffee+Makers&pqatl=google LA Times] {{Wayback|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/access/66382871.html?dids=66382871:66382871&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jan+08%2C+1989&author=DAVID+LASKER&pub=Los+Angeles+Times+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&desc=AROUND+HOME+Chemex+Coffee+Makers&pqatl=google |date=20121104101326 }}, Jan 8, 1989.</ref><ref>[https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F50B14FA345F1A7B93C5A9178AD95F4D8585F9 New York Times] {{Wayback|url=https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F50B14FA345F1A7B93C5A9178AD95F4D8585F9 |date=20131023060526 }} Nov 7, 1959</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.moma.org/collection/|title=The Collection - MoMA|website=The Museum of Modern Art|accessdate=2020-10-14|archive-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516121310/http://www.moma.org/collection/details.php?theme_id=10130|dead-url=no}}</ref>

